        <mxCell id="7qMv6wPczO1rlt5rlKoB-14" value="In CopyOnWriteArrayList each modification creates a fresh copy, so no thread can see a partially modified list. Whenever write happens create a copy (copy-on-write)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
