        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mriFYcUJs7z9-BHMGoYr-10" value="Whenever we write:&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;ArrayList&amp;lt;String&amp;gt; list = new ArrayList&amp;lt;&amp;gt;();&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;Initially an empty array is created&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;elementData = {}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;size=0&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="52.5" y="-550" width="350" height="90" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mriFYcUJs7z9-BHMGoYr-12" value="When we add any elements :&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;list.add(&quot;A&quot;);&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;list.add(&quot;B&quot;)&lt;/b&gt;;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;On the first insertion ArrayList created an internal array with capacity 10.&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="57.5" y="-470" width="445" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mriFYcUJs7z9-BHMGoYr-13" value="&lt;div&gt;Index&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Value&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;0&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; A&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; B&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;null&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;null&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;9&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;null&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="37.5" y="-380" width="165" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mriFYcUJs7z9-BHMGoYr-15" value="size = 2&lt;div&gt;capacity =10&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="252.5" y="-370" width="90" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="mriFYcUJs7z9-BHMGoYr-16" value="When Array becomes full that means the capacity = 10 and size =10 and if we add new element like &lt;b&gt;list.add(&quot;K&quot;);&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;ArrayList creates a new bigger Array with growth formula new capacity = old capacity * 1.5&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;10 -&amp;gt;15&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;15-&amp;gt;22&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;22-&amp;gt;33&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Creates new Array&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Copies old elements&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Adds new elements&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Old array becomes garbage&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="60" y="-260" width="320" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
